# Netlify redirects file for Single Page Application (SPA) routing
# This should be placed in your public folder as "_redirects" (no file extension)

# Handle client-side routing - redirect all requests to index.html
# The 200 status code tells Netlify to serve index.html but keep the original URL
/*    /index.html   200

# Optional: Redirect HTTP to HTTPS (uncomment if needed)
# http://yourdomain.com/*    https://yourdomain.com/:splat  301!

# Optional: Redirect www to non-www (uncomment if needed)
# https://www.yourdomain.com/*    https://yourdomain.com/:splat  301!